        <div class="msgSubject">What's the best way to earn gold?</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-07-03 10:07:54   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-12781732743308922" id="quote-12781732743308922" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-12781732743308922" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=21&amp;mid=12781732743308922&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=12781732743308922&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_12781732743308922" onclick="followToggle('add','12781732743308922')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
