      <div class="msgContentFrame">I'm pretty new to this game. Anyone has any suggestions on how to earn gold fast?</div>
      <div class="msgFtFrame">
        <div class="msgFtFrameFix"></div>
        <div class="msgReplies"><a href="javascript:scrollTo(0,0);">&#9650; Page top</a> |   <a href="/forum.html?forum=21&amp;mid=12781732743308922&amp;page=1&amp;howmany=50#msg12781732743308922" class="icon-linktothis" rel="nofollow">Link to this post</a>  22 replies</div></div>
