      <div class="msgContentFrame">Take the Mining and Skinning professions.  Sell the stuff on the AH.  Sell your green and better items on the AH.  Some items, like Small Eggs, sell really well.  Cooking mats are generally decent, because they are a pain in the ass to farm if you want to PL an alt's skill.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Dalaran&amp;cn=Yehoshua" rel="external nofollow" title="www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Dalaran&amp;cn=Yehoshua">Yehoshua</a> - Human Death Knight, Dalaran <br /><a href="HTTP://www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Dalaran&amp;cn=Valfodr" rel="external nofollow" title="www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Dalaran&amp;cn=Valfodr">Valfodr</a> - Blood Elf Death Knight, Dalaran <br /><a href="HTTP://www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Dalaran&amp;cn=Hiartuar" rel="external nofollow" title="www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Dalaran&amp;cn=Hiartuar">Hiartuar</a> - Blood Elf Mage, Dalaran</div></div>
