      <div class="msgContentFrame">(1) Take gathering trade skills (herbalism, mining or skinning) and sell stacks of what you gather on the auction house. <br />(2) Keep up to date with the auction house market in your faction to make sure you're making the most money that you can. <br />(3) Don't get suckered into spending your gold as if you were a character from Sex And The City with an unlimited credit card. There are very few things that you <i>need</i> to buy. <br />(4) Have a great time playing. <br /><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><span class="sm"><div class="msgQuote"><div class="source"> Rorschach wrote:</div><div class="orig">For my own part, regret nothing. Have lived life, free from compromise ... and step into the shadow now without complaint.</div></div></span> <br /><span class="sm"><div class="msgQuote"><div class="source"> Mazra wrote:</div><div class="orig">Words like 'thee' and 'thou'. Sometimes you miss them. Now it's all &quot;Hell naw, I ain't seen nuttin' mayn.&quot;</div></div></span> <br /></div></div>
