      <div class="msgContentFrame">Quest and sell all the loot including junk items. If you don't know how to use the auction house, now would be a good time to learn. How much gold, and how fast you can make it depends on your level. There are a few tricks that can get you started like buying certain things from vendors and selling them in the AH to people that don't have the time to go all over the place and get when power leveling professions. </div>
